,proclaim
the truth is
risen
, and all lies
shall
return
into hell. The
second
uttering, now is
born an
apostle
of your own nation, and
the Omnipotent is with him. The words
of the third were,a book full of
illustrious
light is
sent
to you from God; and the
fourth voice was heard to
say
, O
Mahomet
,
we have
sent
thee to be a prophet,
apostle
, and guide to the world.
When the
sent
of God was about three
years old, the
blessed
child retired into a
cave, at the
basis
of mount Uriel; when
the archangel Gabriel, covering his face
with his wings, in awful
respect
