plantations
,
to baptize the unfortunate
African
into your faith, and then
use
your
brother
christians
as brutes of the
desert
.
Here I was
so
abashed
for my country,
I could not
answer
him.
Author
. But you hold a
sensual
paradise
Mollab
. So the doctors of your church
tell you; but a
sensual
heaven is no more
imputable to us than to you. When the
Most
Holy
condescends
to reveal
himself
to man in human language, it
must
be in terms
commensurate
